---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "@/components/layout/Breadcrumbs.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Johnny Pro Handyman Services"
  description="Terms of Service for Johnny Pro Handyman Services. Please read our service terms for professional handyman and home repair work in Utah."
>
  <Breadcrumbs />

  <section class="py-20 bg-linear-to-b from-gray-900 to-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8 font-inter">
        Terms of <span class="text-orange-500">Service</span>
      </h1>

      <div
        class="prose prose-invert prose-orange max-w-none text-gray-300 space-y-8"
      >
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">Last Updated: January 5, 2026</p>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing johnnyprohandyman.com or hiring Johnny Pro Handyman
            Services for any work, you agree to be bound by these Terms of
            Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you
            should not use our services or website.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2. Scope of Services</h2>
          <p>
            Johnny Pro Handyman Services provides home repair, maintenance, and
            improvement services in the state of Utah. This includes but is not
            limited to drywall repair, plumbing fixes, electrical work, and
            general maintenance. I reserve the right to refuse service for
            projects that fall outside my expertise or safety standards.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3. Estimates and Quotes</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              All quotes provided via the website or phone are preliminary
              estimates.
            </li>
            <li>
              Final pricing is determined after an on-site assessment of the
              project scope.
            </li>
            <li>
              Quotes are valid for 30 days from the date of issuance unless
              otherwise specified.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">4. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p>
            Payment is due upon completion of the agreed-upon services. For
            larger projects, a deposit (typically 30-50%) may be required before
            work begins. I accept cash, checks, and digital payments.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
            5. Cancellations and Rescheduling
          </h2>
          <p>
            I value your time and ask that you value mine. Please provide at
            least 24 hours' notice for any cancellations or rescheduling.
            Repeated last-minute cancellations may result in a service fee.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">6. Limited Warranty</h2>
          <p>
            I stand behind my workmanship. Johnny Pro Handyman Services provides
            a 1-year warranty on labor for all repairs. This warranty does not
            cover normal wear and tear, customer-supplied materials that fail,
            or damage caused by external forces.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
            7. Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p>
            Johnny Pro Handyman Services is fully insured in Utah and maintains
            professional standards for all work. I am currently in the process
            of official licensing to further demonstrate my commitment to Utah's
            regulatory standards. However, I am not liable for pre-existing
            structural issues found during repairs or for indirect or
            consequential damages arising from the use of my services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">8. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the
            laws of the State of Utah. Any disputes arising from these terms
            shall be resolved in the courts of Salt Lake County, Utah.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Contact Information</h2>
          <div class="bg-gray-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
            <p><strong>Johnny Pro Handyman Services</strong></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (863) 266-1866</p>
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> johnnyprohandyman.com</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
